metadata.name: I Liked It Till You Started Explaining It
metadata.description:
Enough Said!

Medium: Oil & Acrylic on Canvas  
Dimension of Physical: 2.1x 3.7 ft

One collector will be randomly picked (after all editions are sold) who gets to claim the Original Canvas Painting (Unframed) 

Delivery Info: 
1. Additional charges for shipping to be borne by the collector.  
2. There's an option to get the framed original, shipping charges are usually higher in this scenario.
